issue.title: [CF 830] PTR "Invalid spellID found" error
issue.body:

1x TellMeWhen: Invalid spellID found: 110300 (debuffs - Slowed)! Please report this on TMW"s CurseForge page, especially if you are currently on the PTR!

comments.body:
Thanks for the report. This should fix itself once Blizzard updates the interface number to 50400 (it is still 50300). I suppose I could add in a bit more intelligent checking since they seem to be unusually slow getting that updated this patch.
